{"tid":2369702,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南京街懷高大廈列強檢名單　有人攜行李離開","createTime":"2021-01-17T11:15:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T11:59:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3b5737af7b428c93783f8ca56a36fc08131750ae","tid":2369702,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:15:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570878-20210117.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570878-20210117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=2425adbd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570878-20210117.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ca6867cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570878-20210117.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n油麻地及佐敦一帶小區，再有多幢大廈因有住戶確診新型肺炎，相關大廈的住戶需要接受強制檢測，其中包括南京街懷高大廈。<br />\n<br />\n有尼泊爾籍的住戶說，不知道大廈有人確診，但會按強制檢測的要求做檢測，又說不擔心會被感染。另外，有市民攜帶行李離開大廈，但沒有回應是否搬離住所。"},{"pid":"8ed8da1e4aacdd918406be25bb18d46f57c105d2","tid":2369702,"uid":211323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T11:59:28.000Z","msg":"應該叫d狗守撚住出入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一出就拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}